  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145800/extras/c661bac8b6d7f6e45fe3ab486c7a62c7.avif?t=1727631565\" width=618 height=114 /></span><br>Welcome to \"Parkour is White?\" In this game,  You can switch between a variety of colored platforms and try to complete the levels in the shortest time possible.<br><br>This parkour game challenges players to reach the finish line as quickly as possible, navigating through obstacle-filled courses. Players can throw cards onto platforms to enhance their abilities, such as jumping higher or running faster. Compete against your best times, challenge friends, and climb the leaderboard. It’s a thrilling test of speed and skill.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145800/extras/568d04a897e2a10aafecdcd8a538975a.avif?t=1727631565\" width=618 height=114 /></span><br>We have a leaderboard. Climb to the top!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145800/extras/ca5bdfc0556c84536340e8c04679b6cd.avif?t=1727631565\" width=618 height=114 /></span><br>We have achievements for you to earn!",
